snippet.title: Amber Heard’s Lawyers Are Going At Johnny Depp’s Throat For New GQ Interview
snippet.description:
Amber Heard is fighting back. Amber’s lawyer came to her defense after Johnny Depp spoke with reporters from GQ magazine and addressed the abuse allegations levied against him by his ex-wife, a marriage that lasted only one year.
